headline: New CPC Solution Tackles Growing Liquid Cooling Needs for AI
summary: CPC (Colder Products Company), part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leading manufacturer of connection technologies used in liquid cooling of electronics, has developed a new solution to address growing liquid cooling needs in artificial intelligence (AI) computing.
